<item>
            <title>[LANG-1771]  Incorrect output from ClassUtils.getCanonicalName when input is &quot;[String&quot; in version 3.18.0-SNAPSHOT</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LANG-1771</link>
                <project id="12310481" key="LANG">Commons Lang</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In org.apache.commons.lang3.ClassUtils, the method &quot;public static String getShortCanonicalName(final String canonicalName)&quot; returns an incorrect result when given certain malformed array class name strings. Specifically, for the input &lt;tt&gt;&quot;[String&quot;&lt;/tt&gt;, it incorrectly returns &lt;tt&gt;&quot;short[]&quot;&lt;/tt&gt; instead of the expected &lt;tt&gt;&quot;String[]&quot;&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test Code&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;package&lt;/span&gt; org.apache.commons.lang3;

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.assertEquals;

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;ClassUtilsGetCanonicalName {

    @Test
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; void testGetCanonicalName() {
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// Test &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;case&lt;/span&gt;: Non-empty string with one array dimension
&lt;/span&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; input = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;[&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;;
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; expectedOutput = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;[]&quot;&lt;/span&gt;;
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; actualOutput = ClassUtils.getShortCanonicalName(input);
        assertEquals(expectedOutput, actualOutput);
    }
}
 &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Expected Result: String[]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Actual Result: short[]&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;MacOS Sequoia Version 15.3.2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;JDK 8&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
